name: Git with Karagdon, Meow!
body:
Katherine Reyes is a freelance web developer from Seattle, Washington. She currently holds Bachelors of Arts in Marketing and Information Systems from Seattle University, which is also in Seattle, Washington. (2013)

Also, she loves cats, comic books, ice cream, and skateboarding on sunny days. 

### Projects:
* [2013 - BOCK: The Board Game Clock] (http://karagdon.github.com/bock/index.html) - Uses JavaScript to handle user and timed events.

* [2013 - Beacon Food Forest](http://karagdon.github.com/bffsite/index.html) - Turned [Jill DelSordi](http://www.whitewindowstudios.com)'s design into a fully functional website!

* [2012 - Fighting Pride Fitness](http://karagdon.github.com/Fighting%20Pride%20Fitness/index.html) - Splash page design and code for launch package.

* [2012 - Meridian Valley Lab](http://karagdon.github.com/mvl/mvlimgportolio.png) - Contracted for WordPress redesign and custom administration panels

* [2011 - Atlas Clothing](http://karagdon.github.com/atlas/index.html) -
Website redesign of main page (index.html) and galleries.

### Technical Skills:
* Design: Adobe Photoshop, Adobe Illustrator, Corel Painter Pro
* Web: HTML5, CSS3, JS, PHP, C#, VisualBasic, .Net, MySQL, XML
